data.value: Our robots have been specially crafted to be safe around kids and to cater to specific needs. All come equipped with programming that notifies police in the case of a household fire or break in, keeping you protected even when you’re not home. Recent studies have come out suggesting that the stress relief our robots give can even improve your longevity and activity level as well! Due to a recent spike in popularity, factories have been backed up and there are only two models that are still in stock.
